.TH BDFIMPLODE 1 "2008 Jul 06"
.SH NAME
bdfimplode \- Convert a BDF font into GNU Unifont .hex format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.br
.B bdfimplode
<
.I input-font.bdf
>
.I output-font.hex
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bdfimplode
reads a BDF font from STDOUT and writes GNU Unifont .hex conversion
of the font to STDOUT.
.SH FILES
*.bdf font files
